Hello, 

I took the time to write this here because the honor lvl and how it works upsets me a little bit. I enjoy the way the rewards system works and that people toxic get punished it is very normal. As many people also me i have been toxic and i accept my punishment to honor demotion lvl although it was so easy to get demoted to lvl0 honor it is absolutely terribly hard to get back up i have been lvl0 honor for 3 months now and i got honors in this time and still im lvl0 and also while other people have many friends to play with and gets honor from them all the time and reach lvl5 for us that we dont really play with friends and dont get so easily honor we have to try really hard and still people decide to give it somewhere else probably to their friends so in that logic i will need a year just to reach lvl1 and i really believe this is terrible because spending most of my time in this game this keeps me away and also makes me hopeless thinking why to play i never gonna get not even to lvl2 honor and is dissapointing. 

Thank you for your time and i know its normal what you do but doesnt mean we gonna like it {{champion:17}}
